### A4. GET /api/student/krs/sessions/{id}
**Deskripsi** : Detail sesi KRS beserta daftar kelas yang tersedia, dikelompokkan per mata kuliah
**Auth**       : Required

**Path Params**:
| Param | Type    | Required | Keterangan     |
|-------|---------|----------|----------------|
| id    | integer | required | KRS session ID |

**Query Params**:
| Param      | Type    | Required | Keterangan                         |
|------------|---------|----------|------------------------------------|
| id_subject | integer | optional | Filter kelas berdasarkan mata kuliah|
| search     | string  | optional | Cari nama/kode mata kuliah         |

**Response Sukses (200)**:
```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "message": "Detail sesi KRS berhasil diambil.",
  "data": {
    "session": {
      "id_krs_session": 1,
      "status": "open",
      "opened_at": "2026-05-01T09:00:00.000000Z",
      "notes": "Pembatasan SKS maksimal 24",
      "id_academic_period": 1,
      "academic_period": {
        "id_academic_period": 1,
        "name": "2024/2025 - Genap",
        "is_active": true,
        "start_date": "2025-02-01",
        "end_date": "2025-06-30"
      },
      "total_classes": 45
    },
    "subjects": [
      {
        "id_subject": 1,
        "name_subject": "Pemrograman Web",
        "code_subject": "PRW101",
        "sks": 3,
        "classes": [
          {
            "id_class": 10,
            "code_class": "A",
            "day_of_week": "Senin",
            "start_time": "08:00:00",
            "end_time": "10:00:00",
            "member_class": 30,
            "lecturers": [{ "id_user_si": 20, "name": "Dr. Budi" }]
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

**Response Error (404)**:
```json
{ "status": "error", "message": "Sesi KRS ini tidak sedang open." }
```

