## B. MANAGER KRS — Role: `admin` atau `manager`

**Middleware**: `auth:sanctum` + `role:admin|manager`

---

### B1. GET /api/manager/krs-sessions
**Deskripsi** : Ambil daftar semua sesi KRS dengan filter opsional
**Auth**       : Required

**Query Params**:
| Param               | Type    | Required | Keterangan                      |
|---------------------|---------|----------|---------------------------------|
| status              | string  | optional | `open` atau `closed`            |
| id_academic_period  | integer | optional | Filter per periode akademik     |
| per_page            | integer | optional | Default: 15                     |
| page                | integer | optional | Default: 1                      |

**Response Sukses (200)**:
```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "message": "Daftar sesi KRS berhasil diambil.",
  "data": {
    "current_page": 1,
    "data": [
      {
        "id_krs_session": 1,
        "id_academic_period": 1,
        "status": "open",
        "notes": "Pembatasan SKS maksimal 24",
        "opened_at": "2026-05-01T09:00:00.000000Z",
        "closed_at": null,
        "academic_period": { "id_academic_period": 1, "name": "2024/2025 - Genap", "is_active": true },
        "opener": { "id_user_si": 5, "name": "Manager User" },
        "closer": null,
        "session_classes_count": 45
      }
    ],
    "last_page": 1,
    "per_page": 15,
    "total": 1
  }
}
```

---

### B2. POST /api/manager/krs-sessions
**Deskripsi** : Buka sesi KRS baru (opsional: langsung tambahkan kelas)
**Auth**       : Required

**Request Body**:
```json
{
  "id_academic_period": 1,
  "notes": "Pembatasan SKS maksimal 24",
  "classes": [
    { "id_class": 10 },
    { "id_class": 11 }
  ]
}
```

| Field               | Type    | Required | Keterangan                          |
|---------------------|---------|----------|-------------------------------------|
| id_academic_period  | integer | required | Periode akademik yang aktif         |
| notes               | string  | optional | Catatan sesi, maks 1000 karakter    |
| classes             | array   | optional | Array kelas yang langsung ditambahkan|
| classes[].id_class  | integer | required (jika classes ada) | ID kelas  |

**Response Sukses (201)**:
```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "message": "Sesi KRS berhasil dibuka. 2 kelas telah didaftarkan ke sesi ini.",
  "data": {
    "id_krs_session": 1,
    "id_academic_period": 1,
    "status": "open",
    "notes": "Pembatasan SKS maksimal 24",
    "opened_at": "2026-05-01T09:00:00.000000Z",
    "closed_at": null,
    "academic_period": { "id_academic_period": 1, "name": "2024/2025 - Genap" },
    "opener": { "id_user_si": 5, "name": "Current Manager" },
    "session_classes_count": 2
  }
}
```

**Response Error (422)**:
```json
{ "status": "error", "message": "Periode akademik tidak ditemukan." }
```

---

